The American Civil Liberties Union says quite clearly;

“The Trump administration is choosing to separate families. It’s a policy decision that could be stopped at any time by the president without legislation.”

Separating children from parents can be regarded as a form of torture for children, its effects can last a lifetime. The UK cannot be seen to be condoning this by allowing someone doing this to visit the UK, his visit should be cancelled immediately.
